Sat night around (i think) 2 am..  My wife gently wakes me with a very soft spoken and very kind... &quot;hey....hey!   HEY!&quot;<br>
<br>
It seems I feel asleep at the keyboard. When I looked at the screen, I was standing...staring at the wall in Velks.<br>
<br>
